        </table></div><div class="header-trail" style="font-size: 12px"><div title="trail"><a href="?keys=FGEA-print&amp;mode=TOC">The Founding Era Collection</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=GEWN-print&amp;mode=TOC">The Papers of George Washington Digital Edition</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=GEWN-print-02&amp;mode=TOC">Colonial Series (7 July 174815 June 1775)</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=GEWN-print-02-01&amp;mode=TOC">Volume 1 (7 July 174814 August 1755)</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=GEWN-print-02-01-02&amp;mode=TOC">Documents</a>&gt; From William Trent, 19 February 1754 [letter not found]</div></div></div></div><div class="body-norm entry"><div class="printable-document"><a href="/founders/default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-01-02-0032&amp;printable=yes" style="font-weight:normal"><img style="border:0; vertical-align:text-bottom;" src="/img-ML/document-print.png" alt=""/> printable version</a><div class="header-arrows"><div class="header-comp-C1"><a class="point-prev" href="?keys=GEWN-print-02-01-02-0031" title="From Robert Dinwiddie, January 1754"></a></div><div class="header-comp-C2"></div><div class="header-comp-C3"><a class="point-next" href="?keys=GEWN-print-02-01-02-0033" title="From Christopher Gist, 23 February 1754 [letter not found]"></a></div></div><form style="display:inline" action="Utilities/goto-page-in-current-volume.xqy">
